		<div class="comment-body"><p>Hi Raigan,</p>
<p>Yes, the technique you describe will work &#8211; its basically about making sure the things you want to collide are in the same &#8216;space&#8217;, using a wrapped delta like you suggest is one way of doing that <img src="http://www.wildbunny.co.uk/blog/wp-includes/images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" class="wp-smiley" /> </p>
<p>Cheers, Paul.</p>
</div>

